{"id":162,"parent_id":158,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":162,"title":"2 Corinthians 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Cor.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","Gospel light shines on the Saints—Mortal trials are nothing as contrasted with eternal glory."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.1","order":"03.10.004.18597"},["b","1"],"Therefore seeing we have this ministry, as we have received",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"mercy"],", we faint not;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.2","order":"03.10.004.18598"},["b","2"],"But have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"renounced"],"the hidden things of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"dishonesty"],", not walking in craftiness, nor handling the word of God",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"deceitfully"],"; but by manifestation of the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_2d"},"truth"],"commending ourselves to every man’s",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_2e"},"conscience"],"in the sight of God."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.3","order":"03.10.004.18599"},["b","3"],"But if our gospel be hid, it is hid to them that are lost:"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.4","order":"03.10.004.18600"},["b","4"],"In whom the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"god"],"of this",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"world"],"hath",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"blinded"],"the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"minds"],"of them which",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_4e"},"believe not"],", lest the",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_4f"},"light"],"of the glorious gospel of Christ, who is the",["sup","g"],["a",{"href":"fn_4g"},"image"],"of",["sup","h"],["a",{"href":"fn_4h"},"God"],", should shine unto them."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.5","order":"03.10.004.18601"},["b","5"],"For we",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"preach"],"not ourselves, but Christ Jesus the Lord; and ourselves your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"servants"],"for Jesus’ sake."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.6","order":"03.10.004.18602"},["b","6"],"For God, who",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"commanded"],"the light to shine out of darkness, hath",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"shined"],"in our hearts, to",["i","give"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"light"],"of the knowledge of the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"glory"],"of God in the face of Jesus Christ."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.7","order":"03.10.004.18603"},["b","7"],"But we have this treasure in earthen vessels, that the excellency of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"power"],"may be of God, and not of us."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.8","order":"03.10.004.18604"},["b","8"],["i","We are"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"troubled"],"on every side, yet not distressed;",["i","we are"],"perplexed, but not in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"despair"],";"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.9","order":"03.10.004.18605"},["b","9"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Persecuted"],", but not forsaken; cast down, but not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"destroyed"],";"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.10","order":"03.10.004.18606"},["b","10"],"Always bearing about in the body the dying of the Lord Jesus, that the life also of Jesus might be made manifest in our body."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.11","order":"03.10.004.18607"},["b","11"],"For we which live are alway delivered unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"death"],"for Jesus’ sake, that the life also of Jesus might be made manifest in our",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"mortal"],"flesh."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.12","order":"03.10.004.18608"},["b","12"],"So then death worketh in us, but life in you."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.13","order":"03.10.004.18609"},["b","13"],"We having the same spirit of faith, according as it is written, I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"believed"],", and therefore have I spoken; we also believe, and therefore",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"speak"],";"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.14","order":"03.10.004.18610"},["b","14"],"Knowing that he which raised up the Lord Jesus shall raise up us also by Jesus, and shall present",["i","us"],"with you."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.15","order":"03.10.004.18611"},["b","15"],"For all things",["i","are"],"for your sakes, that the abundant grace might through the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"thanksgiving"],"of many redound to the glory of God."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.16","order":"03.10.004.18612"},["b","16"],"For which cause we faint not; but though our outward man perish, yet the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"inward"],["i","man"],"is renewed day by day."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.17","order":"03.10.004.18613"},["b","17"],"For our light",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"affliction"],", which is but for a moment, worketh for us a far more exceeding",["i","and"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"eternal"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_17c"},"weight"],"of glory;"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.18","order":"03.10.004.18614"},["b","18"],"While we look not at the things which are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"seen"],", but at the things which are not seen: for the things which are seen",["i","are"],"temporal; but the things which are not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"seen"],["i","are"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_18c"},"eternal"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.1a","order":"03.10.004.18615"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/12.34"},"Alma 12:34"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.2a","order":"03.10.004.18617"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-qualifying-for"},"TG Priesthood, Qualifying for"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.2b","order":"03.10.004.18619"},["b","2b"],["span.small","GR"],"shame, disgrace.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/honesty"},"TG Honesty"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.2c","order":"03.10.004.18621"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/2.17"},"2 Cor. 2:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.3.3,5"},"1 Thes. 2:3 (3, 5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.2d","order":"03.10.004.18623"},["b","2d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/19.37"},"D&C 19:37"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/75.4"},"75:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"2e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.2e","order":"03.10.004.18625"},["b","2e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conscience"},"TG Conscience"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.4a","order":"03.10.004.18627"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/6.12"},"Eph. 6:12"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/devil"},"TG Devil"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.4b","order":"03.10.004.18629"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/worldliness"},"TG Worldliness"],"."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.4c","order":"03.10.004.18631"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/19.6"},"Alma 19:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/7.12"},"Moro. 7:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/93.39.38-39"},"D&C 93:39 (38–39)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spiritual-blindness"},"TG Spiritual Blindness"],"."],["div",{"id":"4d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.4d","order":"03.10.004.18633"},["b","4d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mind"},"TG Mind"],"."],["div",{"id":"4e","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.4e","order":"03.10.004.18635"},["b","4e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unbelief"},"TG Unbelief"],"."],["div",{"id":"4f","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.4f","order":"03.10.004.18637"},["b","4f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/light-noun"},"TG Light [noun]"],"."],["div",{"id":"4g","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.4g","order":"03.10.004.18639"},["b","4g"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-body-of-corporeal-nature"},"TG God, Body of, Corporeal Nature"],"."],["div",{"id":"4h","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.4h","order":"03.10.004.18641"},["b","4h"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/godhead"},"TG Godhead"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.5a","order":"03.10.004.18643"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/1.11.11-12"},"Gal. 1:11 (11–12)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/missionary-work"},"TG Missionary Work"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.5b","order":"03.10.004.18645"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/9.19"},"1 Cor. 9:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/26.3"},"Alma 26:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.6a","order":"03.10.004.18647"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/33.9"},"Ps. 33:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/2.5.4-5"},"Moses 2:5 (4–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.6b","order":"03.10.004.18649"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/45.9"},"D&C 45:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.6c","order":"03.10.004.18651"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/intelligence"},"TG Intelligence"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/light-of-christ"},"Light of Christ"],"."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/4.6d","order":"03.10.004.18653"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-glory-of"},"TG God, Glory of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures